Revision history for Perl extension NexStarCtl.

0.11  Wed Mar 12 11:28:25 2014
	- ported nexstarctl.pl to windows OS.
	- several bugfixes
	- CGEM mount is now recognized
	- decreased required perl version

      Mon Mar 10 01:25:12 2014
	- initial port to Windows OS.
	- fix several typos

0.10  Sun Mar  9 21:20:07 2014
	- added aux commands tc_get_autoguide_rate
	  tc_set_autoguide_rate tc_get_backlash tc_set_backlash

0.09  Sat Dec  7 22:21:45 2013
	- created nexstarctl.pl tool
	- small fixes to NexStarCtl.pm

0.08  Wed Dec  4 21:36:19 2013
	- tc_set_time() fix misstype in daylight saving logic

      Tue Dec  3 14:38:36 2013
	- tc_set_time() sets date/time to RTC too, if available

0.06.1 Tue Dec  3 12:24:58 2013
	- fix some documentation errors

0.06  Sun Nov  3 13:16:30 2013
